      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ROSEBUD LASS (2) is a very progressive local mare who has won her last 3 starts on the bounce. She is facing a sharp wide in class here, but she has the scope to continue on her winning way. THE BIG FREEZE (5) fought on gamely to score by a long neck here last time out and gets in with less weight for this tougher assignment. He has the pole position, and the hat-trick beckons. OKESUTORA (6) was not far away when finishing fifth at this track last start and he has enough pace to be in this for a long way. Include in all combos. ZESTIMAN (1) went within a nose of victory here at his latest appearance 3 weeks ago, and he is another who is capable of a top 3 finish again. GRINZINGER LASS (4) has continued to improve this prep and, after a solid third last time out, she looks close to another win.",
